wikipedia_page.main: Fanny Vining Davenport (17 July 1829 – 20 July 1891) was an English actress who emigrated to America. After her marriage to the American tragedian Edward Loomis Davenport she was well known as Mrs. E. L. Davenport. Their children included actress Fanny Davenport and actor Harry Davenport; their descendants include actresses Dorothy Davenport and Anne Seymour.
